    'Cartwheel makes safe, science-backed first-aid products to help parents treat and prevent head lice with less stress. Their flagship product ''Nit Happens'' is a Class I 510(k)-exempt OTC gel that is 95.8% effective at killing lice using mild abrasives instead of harsh chemicals. The company also offers a prevention spray and is developing a Heat''Nit medical device for professional use.',
