    'snapshot-company-e-sentience-84aaf17e7f',
    'E-Sentience',
    array['E-Sentience']::text[],
    'MedTech',
    null,
    'Passed',
    'E-Sentience is a platform in which people suffering from mental and physical stress can be better diagnosed, monitored, and treated through innovative wearable technology. The E-Sentience armband is the first patented, wearable device to the market that measures stress levels in real time, directly through the amount of cortisol – also known as “the stress hormone” – in your sweat. Paired with our smartphone app, our wearable goes beyond stress measurement to provide automatic stress management through activating a grounding cooling sensation – one of the most common interventions recommended to manage acute stress when a user’s acute cortisol levels spike. The combination of chronic tracking of cortisol levels and improved moderation of cortisol spikes has been shown to lead to improved physical and mental health.',
    'FY23',
    'http://www.e-sentience.com/',
