    'EdTech',
    null,
    'Passed',
    'Ed Machina is an AI-powered advanced analytics SaaS platform optimizes student retention and engagement in real time.
Problem
Student dissatisfaction, low performance and dropout rates.
We tackle the 3.8B lost of revenue in US as a result of student attrition, and poor student experience, and the 10B LATAM dropout revenue loss.
Solution
AI Powered SaaS platform that predicts student risk from day 1 (70 to 90% assertivity), and recommends and automates actions from different channels, tackling not only the attrition problem, but also scaling the operation lowering its costs.
Traction
First plug and play solution allowing a free trial model converting the largest accounts in LATAM and Spain: Laureate, Lottus, Siglo 21, Europea de Madrid, AP LATAM (OPM), Tec de Monterrey. from 0 to $700ARR in 8 months.',
