    'AdTech',
    'Revenue Stage',
    'Passed',
    'Featured is the generative AI platform for Q&A content creation. We combine human expertise with generative AI to allow any business to answer questions and get featured in 500+ media destinations. We''re growing fast, currently at $400k ARR, and have previously raised $1.1M with VC involvement. We''ve built the generative AI engine with Terkel, and plan to put the engine into Featured.com to accelerate. We''re looking to raise $2M to help fuel that acceleration. How they work based on latest call:Publishers submit questions they want answered and transformed into articles to Featured.comFeatured.com reaches out to professionals who have the experience to answer the questions.The professionals submit answers, and those answers are then transformed into articles sent to the publisher.The publisher credits the professionals, and the professionals get exposure for their personal brand / agency / business.After 3 answers provided, professionals can purchase individuals or team plans to continue answering questions and getting more exposure.',
