  (
    'snapshot-company-flightech-ff350cdfa1',
    'FlighTech',
    array['FlighTech']::text[],
    'AgTech',
    'Pre-Product',
    'Tracking',
    'FlighTech FaaS is a full-stack farming-as-a-service platform helping farmers access insights, inputs, and services.


Problem
Farmers face rising costs, low yields, and fragmented access to inputs, equipment, and processing. Existing precision ag tools provide data but fail to solve execution challenges, leaving farmers unable to act on insights. Small and mid-sized farmers especially struggle with financing, service access, and supply chain gaps that reduce productivity.


Solution
FlighTech FaaS is building a full-stack farming-as-a-service platform that combines precision agriculture data with on-demand inputs, equipment, and processing services. Farmers receive clear recommendations and can easily access what they need, whether by buying, renting, or leasing, helping them boost yields and reduce costs.',
    'FY26',
    'https://www.linkedin.com/company/fligh-technologies/',
    'kmunakan@asu.edu',
    null,
    'e97f92a93c05bc32405c5e2c61e295f35f75b8dfc1b569516d84b260ad26da11',
    true,
