    'snapshot-company-gravitrex-35c6ebf193',
    'Gravitrex',
    array['Gravitrex']::text[],
    'HardTech',
    null,
    'Passed',
    'Gravitrex is a radically new walking-assist device that helps older adults recover mobility after hospitalization / fall
Problem
Over 13MM older adults are hospitalized in the US annually, and 2/3 leave the hospital with a new disability. Walking rehabilitation is challenging because facilities fear falls, and injury to health care providers. But older adults who lose mobility are less likely to remain in their homes and have significantly worse health outcomes.
Solution
Gravitrex is a radically new walking assist-device that supports part of a user’s body weight, making it safer and easier to recover mobility after hospitalization because patients can practice walking as they gradually build their strength, reducing the risk of falling and injury.',
    'FY25,FY26',
    null,
    'kira@gravitrexmobility.com',
