    'Hayes Diagnostics is developing a platform to provide real-time diagnostics through separations science. We aim to reduce the time, the worry, cost, and errors when diagnosing and monitoring patients for cardiac events. When the heart is damaged, it releases markers into the blood. These biomarkers are the go to for risk-stratification and treatment decisions of patients. Better technology is needed to ''see'' these. Technology to measure these markers must be fast, sensitive, and cost effective. The Hayes Diagnostic platform provides faster, real-time results of critical cardiac biomarkers to support physician decision making. Product will be sold to hospitals as a bench top device and sold in razor/razorblade fashion as an in vitro diagnostic device. It is highly scalable as the cartridges can be mass produced and reagents are not required.',
    'FY23',
    'https://sites.google.com/view/hayesdiagnosticsdraft/home',
    'MHayes@asu.edu',
    'SkySong',
    '326de06e5e406be224035ad04c38eca179d4cd7f13f29fa4448f48776c96f53f',
    true,
    'active',
    now()
  ),
