    'snapshot-company-heatkept-5dce2a7edb',
    'HeatKept',
    array['HeatKept']::text[],
    'Consumer',
    'Pre-Product',
    'Passed',
    'HeatKept is developing wireless heated dishware to help households enjoy warm meals longer with innovative technology.
Problem
Many gamers, remote workers, and individuals on the go struggle to keep their meals warm during extended periods, leading to diminished dining satisfaction. Traditional methods like reheating or using insulated containers often fail to maintain optimal food temperatures and can compromise food quality.
Solution
HeatKept believes your dishware should be as high tech as the rest of your life. We’ve designed wireless heated dishware to keep your food warm while you deal with the distractions of today’s life-style. Our first product, the HeatKept plate, is easy to use with touch-sensitive temperature control, a food safety system, and is dishwasher-safe.',
    'FY25',
