    'snapshot-company-memory-lane-games-c2081a1554',
    'Memory Lane Games',
    array['Memory Lane Games', 'Memory', 'Lane', 'Games']::text[],
    'HealthTech',
    'MVP',
    'Passed',
    'Turning memories into games (personalized games-as-medicine). Often, the simplest ideas are best.
With our accessible Reminiscence app (90K downloads in 134 counties), you can play frustration-free games
and reminisce (talk!) with your Mum or Dad on the city they grew up in (“What was the name of this theater on
Main Street?”) or their own family ("What is the name of your eldest son?") or a game ranging from music to
movies, classic cars to cats ‘n dogs, foods to Frank Sinatra, with localized content for 10+ countries. We support
the creation of personalized games using the individual''s own life story and photographs, all designed to trigger
positive memories and foster improved communications. No specialist skill or training is needed for a carer or
