    'Tracking',
    'We provide development and applications of precision probiotics to intervene health complications related to metabolism dysregulation. Currently, our products under development mainly include MetabioticsTM-Glucose Control and Cancer Control, which provide novel and effective approaches for management of type 2 diabetes and colon cancer, respectively.',
