    'CleanTech',
    'MVP',
    'Tracking',
    'Developer of a carbon sequestering platform intended to provide concrete admixtures and ingredients for durable carbon segregation in the built environment. The company''s platform helps to reduce the embodied carbon in concrete production with Solid Carbon''s technology to durably sequester biogenic carbon into the built environment, enabling customers and businesses to reverse the damaging impacts of construction on the climate.',
