  (
    'snapshot-company-sworn-ai-689a787158',
    'Sworn AI',
    array['Sworn AI', 'Sworn']::text[],
    'AI & ML',
    null,
    'Tracking',
    'Law enforcement officers dedicate their lives to protect our communities, but their well-being often goes unaddressed. At SWORN.ai, we’re changing that. Our mission: Deliver cutting-edge technology that provides law enforcement leaders with real-time data and tools, transforming how they measure and manage officer health and wellness. This not only amplifies performance but aids in attracting and retaining top talent.

By fusing technology with law enforcement insights, health and wellness best practices, and business acumen, we optimize workforce effectiveness. With SWORN.ai, agencies shift from reactive to proactive strategies, preemptively addressing health challenges before they escalate. Our data-driven solutions paint a detailed portrait of officer workloads, as well as physical and mental health signatures, paving the way for strategies that minimize stress and maximize productivity. The end result? Enhanced service and better community outcomes.

The ripple effects of a healthier, more informed workforce are undeniable:

• Operational Excellence: Streamlined operations leading to predictable staffing.

• Financial Efficiency: Significant reductions in overtime costs and hiring expenses.

• Risk Mitigation: Fewer legal liabilities with a fit and well-prepared force.

Whether you''re seeking to enhance an existing wellness program or start anew, SWORN.ai delivers unparalleled resilience and operational excellence to your team, ensuring communities receive the best service possible.

Discover the difference SWORN.ai can make. For a demo or more details, visit sworn.ai or reach out at sales@sworn.ai.',
    'FY24',
    'https://www.sworn.ai/',
    null,
    'Plug and Play',
    '4a6ed63844e4da29cf1010a25559d4ad28ee1647607d96fd38e327c0964e61d8',
    true,
    'active',
